3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses deep learning techniques, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence, to diagnose lung cancer. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for image classification, which is a subfield of neural computing. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with medical image analysis, which involves retrieving relevant information from medical images.
